# Phase 34 · AI Trader / Master Meta Mega Addendum

# Phase 34 · Master Meta Mega AI Trader Control Plane

Goal:
Upgrade the Phase 33 AI Trader Simulation Layer into a full simulation-grade AI Trader Control Plane.

Hard safety policy:

- Do not enable live trading.
- Do not add broker live order execution.
- Do not bypass Guardian Risk.
- Do not bypass TradingService, ExecutionEngine, SignalValidationService, RBAC, audit logs, event bus, dry-run mode, or backtesting gates.
- All order execution must remain dry-run / paper-trading only.
- Any UI execution button must visibly say simulation-only or dry-run only.
- Any API execution path must force dry_run=true.
- Do not add high-risk financial advice wording.
- Do not claim guaranteed profit.

Backend scope:

- `backend/app/ai_trader/registry.py`
- `backend/app/ai_trader/features.py`
- `backend/app/ai_trader/service.py`
- `backend/app/api/ai_trader.py`
- `backend/tests/test_ai_trader_phase34.py`

Default strategies:

- `trend_momentum_v1`
- `mean_reversion_v1`
- `volatility_breakout_v1`
- `conservative_guarded_v1`

API:

- `GET /api/ai-trader/status`
- `GET /api/ai-trader/strategies`
- `POST /api/ai-trader/signal`
- `POST /api/ai-trader/compare`
- `POST /api/ai-trader/paper-trade`

Frontend scope:

- AI Trader Control Plane card on XAU dashboard
- strategy selector
- symbol/timeframe/min-confidence controls
- generated signal state
- strategy comparison table
- dry-run-only paper-trade button
- no live trading button

Validation:

```bash
cd backend
source .venv/bin/activate
python -m ruff check app tests
python -B -m pytest -q

cd ../frontend
source ~/.nvm/nvm.sh
nvm use 20
npm test
npm run build
```
